<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
  body { font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #222; line-height: 1.7; }
  .letterhead { text-align: center; border-bottom: 3px solid #361963; padding-bottom: 16px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
  .company-name { font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; color: #361963; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .company-address { font-size: 11px; color: #666; }
  .ref-line { font-size: 11px; color: #888; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .subject { font-weight: bold; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 15px; text-decoration: underline; }
  .content p { margin-bottom: 12px; text-align: justify; }
  .signature { margin-top: 60px; }
  .signature-line { border-top: 1px solid #333; width: 200px; margin-top: 50px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="letterhead">
    <div class="company-name">{{companyLegalName}}</div>
    <div class="company-address">{{companyAddress}}</div>
  </div>

  <div class="ref-line">Date: {{today}} &nbsp;|&nbsp; Ref: REL/{{employeeCode}}/{{currentYear}}</div>

  <div class="subject">RELIEVING LETTER</div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Dear <strong>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</strong>,</p>

    <p>This is to confirm that you have been relieved from your duties at <strong>{{companyLegalName}}</strong> with effect from <strong>{{formatDate lastWorkingDate}}</strong>.</p>

    <p>You were associated with us from <strong>{{formatDate dateOfJoining}}</strong> to <strong>{{formatDate lastWorkingDate}}</strong>, serving as <strong>{{designation}}</strong> in the <strong>{{department}}</strong> department.</p>

    <p>All dues have been settled as per company policy, and you have completed all exit formalities including the clearance process.</p>

    <p>We acknowledge that you have returned all company property and assets assigned to you during your tenure.</p>

    <p>We wish you all the best in your future career.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="signature">
    <p>For <strong>{{companyLegalName}}</strong></p>
    <div class="signature-line"></div>
    <p>Authorized Signatory</p>
    <p>HR Department</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
